 tunnel to check out how lively the &quot;market central&quot; of this server is. <br><br>It's dead. <br><br>Completely abandoned. <br><br>Not a single soul was on that ledge of the tunnel overlooking East Commonlands. <br><br>I've played in 2 other servers and they both had market central based in the tunnels. Even in the wee hours of the night, there are always a couple dozen people there at the least. <br><br>So where would I find it on this server? <br><br>/boggle<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umellandra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mellandra</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 59<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 4:03:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where is market central on FV? It sure aint EC tunnels</span><hr size=1> Greater Faydark sounds like the place to be.  However, for scum such as you necromantic types I'd say you're better of leaving the beautiful Feydwer and never returning.  I'm sure the dark elves *spit* would take you in. <p><p><b>Mellandra Freespirit</b>,<i>(Court of the Crosswinds)</i>, wizard and follower of Tunare</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubjond.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 258<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 4:14:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Odd, I've never seen ..</span><hr size=1> .. EC tunnel as a market spot on any server -- only played on a few others, though.  I always thought (and found) G.Faydark to be the most active, but the very best spot is the market-board here on the web.<br><br>One thing to be aware of on FV: /auction only has a very limitted range.  It only reaches as far as /yell.  So, you need to stand at one of the common spots.  In order, I'd say they're G.Fay spires, Kelethin bank (yuck!), and Felwithe entrance.  FP bank occasionally has some action, too.<br><br>BTW, I just noticed the small /auc range the other day when I happened to have both comps up in the same zone.  One char could hear the /auc at the FP bank.  The other char just beyond the jeweler could not.  I repeated the test in the other direction -- same thing.  It wasn't just a random packet-drop. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uroninsenshi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RoninSenshi</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia</span><br>  Posts: 310<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 4:23:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Kanji.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Odd, I've never seen ..</span><hr size=1> YOu'll come to love the empty East Commonlands. <p><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif"><A HREF="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo">Shintou Shinai</A>, A Follower of Lanys T'Vyl, and her Primodial Malice.<BR>Firiona Vie (Roleplaying Preffered, Powergaming Approved!) Server.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left>