=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where is market central on FV? It sure aint EC tunnels</span><hr size=1> Bjond, <br><br>EC has been the market center for the other servers I've played on.... that's because they were regular blue servers, and thus the good races AND the evil races always co-mingled with each other. <br><br>And where is the most convenient location for that co-mingling? <br><br>East Commons Tunnel -- the neutral midway point between Neriak and Freeport.  The tunnel is also a very &quot;neutral&quot; place, where both evil and good races may pass thru it unharmed by any NPC.  The only exception is that Sergeant Slate is occasionally trained to the tunnel entrance.... whereupon he can be seen slaughtering a handful of Troll, Iksar and Ogre newbies.  But the high level players end up taking him down quick.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umaladominus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maladominus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 5:58:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where is market central on FV? It sure aint EC tunnels</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I cant believe no one has added this info to this post.<br><br>On FV you can ONLY use /auction in city zones... that is why EC is a ghost town <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>Useful information. Thanks Roawen. <br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umellandra.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mellandra</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 61<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 7:11:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where is market central on FV? It sure aint EC tunnels</span><hr size=1> /auction is also NOT limited to /yell range.  It's /shout that's been reduced to /yell range.  /auction is a zonewide message but only available in city zones (hence no-one in EC auctioning).<br><br>I suspect that over time (and once they've got the code sorted) the Bazaar on Luclin will become <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> the</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> place to trade. <p><p><b>Mellandra Freespirit</b>,<i>(Court of the Crosswinds)</i>, wizard and follower of Tunare</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubjond.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 259<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 9:00:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where is market central on FV? It sure aint EC tunnels</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> And where is the most convenient location for that co-mingling?  East Commons Tunnel -- the neutral midway point between Neriak and Freeport.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->I played inky and ogre and iksar on a normal blue.  By far the easiest access was G.Fay -- due to the wizard spires.  There's no nearby gate for EC, so no one used it.  Guess each server has it's quirks.<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> auction is also NOT limited to /yell range. It's /shout that's been reduced to /yell range. /auction is a zonewide message.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->No, at least not in Freeport.  I tested it personally.  I had two comps up, one just past the jeweler and one at the bank.  Neither could hear the other's auc's until I moved into range.  This was a big surprise for me, since I had previously thought only /shout was reduced.  I didn't check to see if it was precisely /yell range, but the range is very short; /auc is most definitely NOT zone-wide.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=castinareleas>CastinarEleas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 80<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/22/02 9:07:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1161.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> auction range</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> No, at least not in Freeport. I tested it personally. I had two comps up, one just past the jeweler and one at the bank. Neither could hear the other's auc's until I moved into range. This was a big surprise for me, since I had previously thought only /shout was reduced. I didn't check to see if it was precisely /yell range, but the range is very short; /auc is most definitely NOT zone-wide.  <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>I know when FV started, Auction was zone-wide and city zones only. However, I